  "StockRole": "Heavy Sniper",
  "YangsThoughts": "In the late hours of the Amaris Civil War, there were rumors of an advanced stealth mech head hunter equipped with four gauss rifles. Now if this is true or just an urban legend, I couldn't tell you Boss. What I can tell you is that someone tried to impersonate this legend with a Nightstar. 4 Light Gauss rifles make this a very capable direct fire Long Range Mech. An AMS makes it survivable against Long Range Missiles. Where they got the Clan-XL Engine from though, that's a mystery - Hell, it even has a full SLDF-spec Warfare Suite. This 'Mech is filled with a solid mix of IS and Clan technology to make an actual nightmare. Don't ask me about the name of this Mech we've started calling \"Number 3\". It's got 13 threes in its 17-digit serial number and the number '3' carved into the emergency ejection button.",
